Class Review

java.lang.Object
application.Review
public class Review extends Object
Represents a review made by a reviewer on an answer.

    • Review

      public Review(String reviewId, String answerId, String reviewer, String content, Timestamp createdAt, String parentReviewID)
      Creates a Review instance.
      Parameters:
      reviewId - unique review id
      answerId - associated answer id
      reviewer - reviewer's username
      content - review body
      createdAt - timestamp of creation
      parentReviewID - id of parent review (if any)
